			title: "Beyond the Map"
			icon: "explorerscompass:explorers_compass"
			subtitle: "The world is bigger than it looks"
			description: [
				"§6You cleared the End. You've earned the right to go deeper.§r"
				"§fThe overworld holds structures your early-game self couldn't handle —"
				"§fmassive procedural dungeons from §eWhen Dungeons Arise§f,"
				"§fcompletely rebuilt vanilla structures from the §eYUNG's§f suite,"
				"§fand hidden dimensions waiting for End-tier gear."
				""
				"§ePrerequisite:§r"
				"§7• §6Dragon Slayer ✦§7 (Ch 3) — you have End-tier armor and weapons."
				"§7• §6Archmage Spellbook§7 (Ch 1) recommended — spells are strong in dungeons."
				"§7• §6Silent Gear max-grade tools§7 (Ch 2.7) — durability matters."
				""
				"§eExplorer's Compass (reward):§r"
				"§7• §eRight-click§7 → select a structure type to search for."
				"§7• Shows distance and direction to the nearest matching structure."
				"§7• §eUse it§7 to find When Dungeons Arise targets and YUNG's structures."
				""
				"§a► Loot your first WDA dungeon. Mark done."
			]
			dependencies: ["000D001C"]
		}

