			icon: "minecraft:iron_door"
			description: [
				"§6When Dungeons Arise generates massive multi-floor dungeons§r"
				"§6scattered across the overworld — each one is a full adventure.§r"
				""
				"§eDungeon types (largest to smallest):§r"
				"§7• §eThornborn Towers§7 — tall spired fortresses, 6–8 floors, elite loot."
				"§7• §eShiraz Palace§7 — wide desert palace with trap corridors."
				"§7• §eFrozen Lighthouse§7 — coastal structure with ice and undead."
				"§7• §eForgotten Wastelands§7 — open ruined complex, many mob types."
				"§7• §eSmaller WDA dungeons§7 — scattered outposts, each with a loot room."
				""
				"§eFinding them:§r"
				"§7• §eExplorer's Compass§7 — search for 'when_dungeons_arise' structure tags."
				"§7• §eTraveler's Compass§7 — navigate to discovered POI coordinates."
				"§7• §eXaero's World Map§7 — WDA dungeons appear as icons after discovery."
				""
				"§ePreparation:§r"
				"§7• §eFull armor§7 — these dungeons scale mob difficulty."
				"§7• §eArs Nouveau§7 Blink glyph — escape trap rooms instantly."
				"§7• §eComforts sleeping bag§7 — set spawn inside the dungeon."
				""
				"§a► Reach the final floor (deepest loot room). Mark done."
