				"§6Deeper and Darker massively expands Ancient City content —§r"
				"§6new rooms, new blocks, and the Warden reworked into a true§r"
				"§6stealth challenge.§r"
				""
				"§eWhat Deeper and Darker adds to Ancient Cities:§r"
				"§7• §eOtherside Portal§7 — a dimension portal found in the deepest Ancient City rooms."
				"§7• §eNew sculk structures§7 — sculk libraries, echo shard deposits, reinforced walls."
				"§7• §eNew blocks§7 — Sculk Bone, Gloom, Reinforced Deepslate variants."
				"§7• §eWarder variants§7 — additional mob types guarding deeper sections."
				""
				"§eSurviving the Ancient City:§r"
				"§7• §eSneaking only§7 — no sprinting, no falling damage, no mob aggro."
				"§7• §eArs Nouveau Silence glyph§7 — reduces your noise radius significantly."
				"§7• §eWool blocks§7 in your hotbar — cover Shriekers before approaching."
				"§7• §eNight Vision§7 — the City is pitch dark. Wool-covered torches work."
				"§7• §eIf the Warden spawns§7 — use Blink glyph to escape, don't fight it."
				""
				"§eSwift Sneak enchant (reward):§r"
				"§7• Move at full crouch speed — essential for future City runs."
				""
				"§a► Loot the central chest room without summoning the Warden. Mark done."
